Tum recursion aur backtracking **bahut hi deep level** pe samajhne ki koshish kar rahe ho â€” aur iss tarah dekhna sabse best approach hai. Agar chaho toh main ye **code trace karte hue ek animated recursion tree ya call stack diagram bhi bana sakta hoon.**

